\begin_layout Standard
数据点的分布并不一定呈一条直线, 此时可用多项式拟合.
 对于给定的一组数据
\begin_inset Formula $(x_{i},y_{i})(i=1,2,…,n)$
\end_inset

,寻求次数不超过
\begin_inset Formula $m(m\lessdot n)$
\end_inset

的多项式
\begin_inset Formula $y(x)=a_{0}+a_{1}x+a_{2}x^{2}+…+a_{m}x^{m}$
\end_inset

来拟合所给定的数据, 与线性拟合类似, 使偏差的平方和
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
Q=\sum_{i=1}^{n}\left(y_{i}-\sum_{j=0}^{m}a_{j}x_{i}^{j}\right)^{2}
\]

\end_inset

最小.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
同样适用向量的形式表示这些数据.
 我们设
\begin_inset Formula ${\bf a}=(a_{0},a_{1},a_{2},\cdots,a_{m})'\in\R^{(m+1)\times1}$
\end_inset

为多项式前面的系数; 
\begin_inset Formula ${\bf y}=(y_{1},y_{2},\cdots,y_{n})'\in\R^{n\times1}.$
\end_inset

实际上, 只要将样本的矩阵
\begin_inset Formula ${\bf X}$
\end_inset

改变为
\begin_inset Formula ${\bf X}=\begin{bmatrix}1 & x_{1} & x_{1}^{2} & \cdots & x_{1}^{m}\\
1 & x_{2} & x_{2}^{2} & \cdots & x_{2}^{m}\\
\vdots & \vdots & \vdots & \ddots & \vdots\\
1 & x_{n} & x_{n}^{2} & \cdots & x_{n}^{m}
\end{bmatrix}\in\R^{n\times(m+1)}$
\end_inset

