\begin_layout Example
对于
\begin_inset Formula $ae^{-bx}$
\end_inset

而言, 两边取对数得
\begin_inset Formula $\underbrace{\ln y}_{Y}=\underbrace{\ln a}_{a_{0}}\underbrace{-b}_{a_{1}}x$
\end_inset

.
 可得到线性模型.
 由于
\begin_inset Formula $n=6,m=1$
\end_inset

, 法方程组为
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\begin{cases}
6a_{0}+a_{1}\sum_{i=1}^{6}x_{i}=\sum_{i=1}^{6}Y_{i}\\
a_{0}\sum_{i=1}^{6}x_{i}+a_{1}\sum_{i=1}^{6}x_{i}^{2}=\sum_{i=1}^{6}x_{i}Y_{i}
\end{cases}
\]

\end_inset

计算相应的数据, 得到
\begin_inset Formula $\left\{ \begin{aligned}6a_{0}+7.5a_{1}=-2.43302\\
7.5a_{0}+13.75a_{1}=-5.714112
\end{aligned}
\right.$
\end_inset

.
 得
\begin_inset Formula $a_{0}=0.562302,a_{1}=-0.772282.$
\end_inset

于是
\begin_inset Formula $a=e^{-bx}$
\end_inset

, 得到
\begin_inset Formula $a=e^{0.562302}=1.754708,$
\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula $b=0.772282$
\end_inset

.
 其拟合指数函数为
\begin_inset Formula $y=1.754708e^{-0.772282x}$
\end_inset

.
